description:
"I have slept with more men than she has!" Dennis joked, referring to his 24-year-old girlfriend.
"She likes to tease me about that."
Isaac laughed. He was wrapped in Dennis' muscular arms and you could tell that he was ready.
Isaac has started to refer to himself as "The Power Bottom."
"Now that I know what 'power bottom' means," Dennis said. "It makes sense."
"We did have to teach him!" Isaac said.
title: Dennis & Isaac
